thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/author-Ry0GXj_uifS6AejvZUIukQ">Thanh Tâm tài nhân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Linh-V%E1%BA%ADn/Thu-H%E1%BB%93-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-jxn87ZZRFzwNL0Dv_GL43Q">Thu Hồ hành kỳ 1 - 秋胡行其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Linh-V%E1%BA%ADn/author-7k3dwdcuJKTWbJGjPLm2kg">Tạ Linh Vận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/Ti%E1%BB%83u-y%E1%BA%BFn-quan-k%E1%BB%B9/poem-3SFnzuswvWqUeqNdjD1qTg">Tiểu yến quan kỹ - 小宴觀妓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-vpkhTYu5I0Ga1J2slJa8Pw">Trường hận ca - 長恨歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/author-LhlsyQN9Bp8xEaFjAVEqow">Vương Kiều Loan</a>)<br></div>	</div>
